metadata.name: SEED - WATER 1/2022
metadata.description: Life begins with water and what you water grows. SEED is excited to announce our first NFT project—WATER—a community membership NFT that bridges together art, tech, fashion, education, nature, and culture. WATER collectors are at the forefront of the SEED NFT ecosystem, and will receive exclusive access to the EARTH, AIR, and FIRE NFT drops. Collectors will need all four of these element NFTs to plant a seed in the future. Holding of the Water NFT will also give you the ability to unlock access to exclusive products, Oasis experiences, giveaways, capsule collections, discounts, collabs, and much more.
